text: Hello, is there some standard "under development" language / caveat that Linux Foundation uses in its product documentation? Something about what is guaranteed in a given release or not; I'm interested in this statement for Hyperledger Fabric 0.5.
Bitcoin example: see the "experimental" heading / text: <https://bitcoin.org/en/you-need-to-know>
